rows.label: tlk41700161_01_msg0001
rows.name:
You're the passengers from the ship
that came from Superbia, right?

rows.label: tlk41700161_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Are you heading to Iyasaki
Village? If so, you'll need
to go through the Cloudway.

rows.label: tlk41700161_01_msg0003
rows.name:
There are two Cloudways. The closer
one is the Lud Cloudway, but that
one's crawling with monsters.

rows.label: tlk41700161_01_msg0004
rows.name:
If you want to go safely, it's best to
cross from Baldotas Isle to Daram Isle
and proceed through the Norem Cloudway.
